1383
01:32:16,680 --> 01:32:19,840
I was writing about the one thing
you wanted to have total control over:

1384
01:32:20,040 --> 01:32:21,920
Collins and Morris.

1385
01:32:23,400 --> 01:32:27,320
You made me abandon any thought
of trying to contact Lanny.

1386
01:32:27,880 --> 01:32:30,200
You made me feel like I was
less than nothing to him...

1387
01:32:30,400 --> 01:32:32,480
...because you were playing
your own complex game.

1388
01:32:32,680 --> 01:32:38,120
And what exactly was this complex
game I was playing, Miss O'Connor?

1389
01:32:56,000 --> 01:32:57,600
You were in the room.

1390
01:32:58,880 --> 01:33:00,520
That night.

1391
01:33:01,240 --> 01:33:03,840
Lanny had a robe.
He dropped it on the bed.

1392
01:33:04,040 --> 01:33:06,520
After Maureen asked for money...

1393
01:33:06,720 --> 01:33:08,600
...the wallet was on top.
It had been folded.

1394
01:33:08,800 --> 01:33:12,160
Well, I always, always arranged
Mr. Morris' things.

1395
01:33:12,360 --> 01:33:15,480
After he went to bed.
You were there before.

1396
01:33:15,680 --> 01:33:18,720
How would I get out?
All three doors were chain-locked.

1397
01:33:36,320 --> 01:33:38,400
Through Vince's room.

1398
01:33:39,800 --> 01:33:41,280
Then, the next morning...

1399
01:33:41,480 --> 01:33:44,680
<i>...you must have chain-locked the
door before you went to wake him up.</i>

1400
01:33:48,600 --> 01:33:50,640
Fuck!

1401
01:33:53,600 --> 01:33:55,880
Lanny let me read the first chapter.

1402
01:33:56,080 --> 01:33:58,320
Vince sent me the second.

1403
01:34:00,840 --> 01:34:02,600
And you stole this.

1404
01:34:02,800 --> 01:34:04,160
To whet my appetite.

1405
01:34:27,680 --> 01:34:29,320
<i>I wanna write.</i>

1406
01:34:29,520 --> 01:34:31,360
<i>I wanna be a journalist.</i>

1407
01:34:31,960 --> 01:34:34,880
<i>So I could either
use this information...</i>

1408
01:34:35,720 --> 01:34:37,600
<i>...or I could use a lot of money.</i>

1409
01:34:37,800 --> 01:34:40,080
Is that why you killed her?

1410
01:34:41,320 --> 01:34:42,520
To protect them?

1411
01:34:49,560 --> 01:34:53,280
<i>For 15 years...</i>

1412
01:34:53,480 --> 01:34:56,400
<i>...he tormented Vince and Lanny.</i>

1413
01:34:59,840 --> 01:35:03,360
<i>He could never blackmail Vince
while Sally Sanmarco was alive...</i>

1414
01:35:04,240 --> 01:35:08,440
<i>...so he waited until Sally died
to activate his retirement plan:</i>

1415
01:35:10,920 --> 01:35:13,880
<i>A million dollars from Vince.</i>

1416
01:35:14,600 --> 01:35:18,760
<i>A million dollars for the same tape
he offered to me.</i>

1417
01:35:23,480 --> 01:35:27,200
<i>He would never get his money,
and I would never see him again.</i>

1418
01:35:33,000 --> 01:35:35,520
<i>He had taken her life...</i>

1419
01:35:35,720 --> 01:35:38,360
<i>...and with it her mother's heart...</i>

1420
01:35:39,000 --> 01:35:41,200
<i>...and her father's mind.</i>

1421
01:35:42,760 --> 01:35:44,200
<i>And now...</i>

1422
01:35:44,400 --> 01:35:47,520
<i>...all that remained
of Maureen O'Flaherty...</i>

1423
01:35:47,720 --> 01:35:51,560
<i>...was a tree
in her mother's garden.</i>

1424
01:36:05,720 --> 01:36:08,840
Your daughter learned something
about Vince Collins...

1425
01:36:09,000 --> 01:36:11,520
...that he didn't want anyone to know.

1426
01:36:11,800 --> 01:36:13,440
Because of that...

1427
01:36:13,640 --> 01:36:15,120
...she was killed.

1428
01:36:15,320 --> 01:36:18,360
If it's of any small comfort,
she probably didn't suffer.

1429
01:36:18,920 --> 01:36:22,400
I want people
to know about this man.

1430
01:36:22,960 --> 01:36:25,640
I want them to know
why he killed her.

1431
01:36:30,760 --> 01:36:32,840
There is someone in all this...

1432
01:36:33,040 --> 01:36:35,040
...who is totally innocent
of any involvement...

1433
01:36:35,240 --> 01:36:37,080
...in the events of that night...

1434
01:36:37,280 --> 01:36:41,920
...but whose life will be made infinitely
worse if I tell the truth at this time.

1435
01:36:42,920 --> 01:36:46,280
I wanna protect this person
from any further pain.

1436
01:36:49,200 --> 01:36:51,080
I promise you-

1437
01:36:51,640 --> 01:36:55,000
I promise you I will write down
the truth that I've learned...

1438
01:36:55,200 --> 01:36:58,080
...but I have to let matters lie
until this person has died...

1439
01:36:58,280 --> 01:37:00,360
...and the truth
can no longer touch them.

1440
01:37:05,360 --> 01:37:08,320
<i>I saw no indication on her face...</i>

1441
01:37:08,520 --> 01:37:11,000
<i>...that she knew
I was talking about her.</i>

1442
01:37:43,400 --> 01:37:45,880
You're a very special girl.

1443
01:37:53,680 --> 01:37:56,040
Forgive me.

